| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-0734 — Recovery Inhibition (spacebears)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 6835bd70-f870-5c5e-a0cb-54e828adcc7e"
